Sample HR Policy Document

Introduction
This document outlines the HR policies for our organization.

Leave Policy
Employees are entitled to 20 days of annual leave per year. Sick leave is 10 days. Maternity leave is 12 weeks.

Salary and Benefits
Salaries are paid monthly. Benefits include health insurance and provident fund contributions.

Code of Conduct
Employees must maintain professionalism. No harassment or discrimination.

IT Support Guidelines
For password resets, contact IT. Software requests should be submitted via the portal.

Company Events
We host annual meetings and quarterly team building activities.

Termination Policy
Notice period is 30 days. Reasons for termination include misconduct.

Training and Development
Ongoing training programs are available to enhance skills.

Diversity and Inclusion
We promote a diverse workplace.

Performance Reviews
Annual reviews are conducted to assess employee performance.

Remote Work
Remote work is allowed subject to approval.

